getRMSEArrays

public  getRMSEArrays(DatasetSparseVector<T> test,
                           java.util.List<T> model,
                           java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Integer> userToModel)

Creates two arrays that can be compared with the RMSE test.

Each array is composed of the sequence of ratings of each user one after the other, so you can expect to start with the ratings given by the first user, followed by the ratings of the following user and so on.

The test set is used as a reference, and only entries in both the test and training sets are considered.

A warning is issued if an entry present in the test set is not present in the training set, as this should be avoided.

Parameters:
test - the test set
model - the model of the training set
userToModel - a map to obtain the corresponding user from the model
Returns:
a pair of arrays that can be compared through the RMSE test
